---
import { changeLanguage, t } from "i18next";
import { Trans } from "astro-i18next/components";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import Layout from "@ui/layouts/Layout.astro";

changeLanguage("es");
---

<Layout title={t('home.pageTitle')}>
  <main class='main'>
    <div class='main__hero'>
      <h1 class='animated slide-up'>
        {t('home.hero.title')}
        <br />
        {t('home.hero.subtitle')}
      </h1>

      <div class='main__hero__description'>
        <p>
          {t('home.hero.description')}
        </p>

        <a href={t('routes.about')} class='callToActions animated reveal-text-up'>
          <span></span>
          {t('home.hero.button')}
          <Icon name='heroicons-outline:arrow-narrow-right' />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='main__image'>
      <img class='animated slide-up' src='' alt='Kevin Parra Photo' />
    </div>
  </main>

  <section class='about'>
    <div class='about__container'>
      <h2 class='animated reveal-text-up'>
        {t('home.about.container1.title')}
      </h2>

      <div class='about__container__text'>
        <p class='animated reveal-text-up'>
          {t('home.about.container1.text1')}
        </p>

        <p class='animated reveal-text-up'>
          <Trans i18nKey='home.about.container1.text2'>
            Con una trayectoria de liderazgo en equipos, he entregado proyectos que impactan a
            usuarios globalmente, especializándome en <strong>React, React Native, Next.js</strong>
            y <strong>Node.js</strong>.
          </Trans>
        </p>

        <p class='animated reveal-text-up'>
          <Trans i18nKey='home.about.container1.text3'>
            Además, tengo experiencia avanzada en crear <strong>experiencias inmersivas 3D</strong
            >, utilizando librerías como <strong>Three.js</strong> y aplicándolas en contextos de realidad
            aumentada y virtual.", "text4": "He trabajado recientemente con estas tecnologías:
          </Trans>
        </p>

        <p class='animated reveal-text-up'>
          {t('home.about.container1.text4')}
        </p>

        <ul class='animated reveal-text-up'>
          <li class='animated slide-up'>JavaScript (ES6+)</li>

          <li class='animated slide-up'>Html - (S)CSS</li>

          <li class='animated slide-up'>React.js</li>

          <li class='animated slide-up'>React Native</li>

          <li class='animated slide-up'>Jest + Enzyme</li>

          <li class='animated slide-up'>react-testing-library</li>

          <li class='animated slide-up'>Tailwind CSS</li>

          <li class='animated slide-up'>PWA's</li>

          <li class='animated slide-up'>Webpack</li>

          <li class='animated slide-up'>Three.js</li>

          <li class='animated slide-up'>WebXR</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='agencies'>
    <div class='agencies__header'>
      <div class='agencies__header__container'>
        <h2 class='animated reveal-text-up'>
          {t('home.agencies.title')}
        </h2>
        <p class='animated reveal-text-up'>
          {t('home.agencies.subtitle')}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='agencies__container'>
      <img
        class='animated reveal-text-up'
        src='../../src/ui/assets/images/static/Portinos.png'
        alt='Portinos logo'
      />
      <img
        class='animated reveal-text-up'
        src='../../src/ui/assets/images/static/Intel.png'
        alt='Intel logo'
      />
      <img
        class='animated reveal-text-up'
        src='../../src/ui/assets/images/static/Kcumen.svg'
        alt='Kcumen logo'
      />
      <img
        class='animated reveal-text-up'
        src='../../src/ui/assets/images/static/Sena.png'
        alt='Sena logo'
      />
      <img
        class='animated reveal-text-up'
        src='../../src/ui/assets/images/static/arcor.png'
        alt='Arcor Logo'
      />
      <img
        class='animated reveal-text-up'
        src='../../src/ui/assets/images/static/Onu.png'
        alt='Onu logo'
      />
      <img
        class='animated reveal-text-up'
        src='../../src/ui/assets/images/static/logoHemav.png'
        alt='Hemav logo'
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
